#~ "With <abbr title=\"Dual Channel Wi-Fi AP Daemon\">Dual Channel WiFi</"
#~ "abbr> you can use two simultaneous Wi-Fi connections to decrease wireless "
#~ "traffic congestion and increase throughput."
